font style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">oder es existiert keine Geplante Abgabe</font></i></div></div></div></div></foreignObject><image x="60" y="712" width="224" height="32" xlink:href="data:image/png;base64,"/></switch></g></g></g><g data-cell-id="4ui51u9nk6TVf3VnQzT0-40"><g transform="translate(0.5,0.5)"><path d="M 577.25 723.26 L 647.25 723.26 L 667.25 743.26 L 667.25 753.26 L 577.25 753.26 L 577.25 723.26 Z" fill="#f5f5f5" stroke="#666666" stroke-miterlimit="10" pointer-events="all" style="fill: rgb(245, 245, 245); stroke: rgb(102, 102, 102);"/><path d="M 647.25 723.26 L 647.25 743.26 L 667.25 743.26" fill="none" stroke="#666666" stroke-miterlimit="10" pointer-events="all" style="stroke: rgb(102, 102, 102);"/></g><g><g><switch><foreignObject style="overflow: visible; text-align: left;" pointer-events="none" width="100%" height="100%" requiredFeatures="http://www.w3.org/TR/SVG11/feature#Extensibility"><div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="display: flex; align-items: unsafe center; justify-content: unsafe flex-start; width: 88px; height: 1px; padding-top: 738px; margin-left: 579px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 0; text-align: left; color: #333333; "><div style="display: inline-block; font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333; line-height: 1.2; pointer-events: all; white-space: normal; word-wrap: normal; "><b>Kassenrezept </b></div></div></div></foreignObject><image x="579" y="731.5" width="88" height="17" xlink:href="data:image/png;base64,"/></switch></g></g></g><g data-cell-id="4ui51u9nk6TVf3VnQzT0-111"><g transform="translate(0.5,0.5)"><path d="M 1117 1236.32 L 1337 1236.32 L 1357 1256.32 L 1357 1346.97 L 1117 1346.97 L 1117 1236.32 Z" fill="#f5f5f5" stroke="#666666" stroke-miterlimit="10" pointer-events="all" style="fill: rgb(245, 245, 245); stroke: rgb(102, 102, 102);"/><path d="M 1337 1236.32 L 1337 1256.32 L 1357 1256.32" fill="none" stroke="#666666" stroke-miterlimit="10" pointer-events="all" style="stroke: rgb(102, 102, 102);"/></g><g><g><switch><foreignObject style="overflow: visible; text-align: left;" pointer-events="none" width="100%" height="100%" requiredFeatures="http://www.w3.org/TR/SVG11/feature#Extensibility"><div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="display: flex; align-items: unsafe center; justify-content: unsafe flex-start; width: 238px; height: 1px; padding-top: 1292px; margin-left: 1119px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 0; text-align: left; color: #333333; "><div style="display: inline-block; font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333; line-height: 1.2; pointer-events: all; white-space: normal; word-wrap: normal; "><b style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Privatrezept</b><div><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">die Geplante Abgabe wird erst dann auf completed gesetzt, wenn die maximale Zahl der Einlösemöglichkeiten erreicht ist. </span></div><div><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;">Die Einlösung muss einem Complete-Type haben, damit der nächste Einlösevorgang in einer anderen Apotheke erfolgen kann.</span></div></div></div></div></foreignObject><image x="1119" y="1242" width="238" height="104" xlink:href="data:image/png;base64,"/></switch></g></g></g><g data-cell-id="4ui51u9nk6TVf3VnQzT0-112"><g transform="translate(0.5,0.5)"><path d="M 1214 753.26 L 1467 753.26 L 1487 773.26 L 1487 893.26 L 1214 893.26 L 1214 753.26 Z" fill="#f5f5f5" stroke="#666666" stroke-miterlimit="10" pointer-events="all" style="fill: rgb(245, 245, 245); stroke: rgb(102, 102, 102);"/><path d="M 1467 753.26 L 1467 773.26 L 1487 773.26" fill="none" stroke="#666666" stroke-miterlimit="10" pointer-events="all" style="stroke: rgb(102, 102, 102);"/></g><g><g><switch><foreignObject style="overflow: visible; text-align: left;" pointer-events="none" width="100%" height="100%" requiredFeatures="http://www.w3.org/TR/SVG11/feature#Extensibility"><div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="display: flex; align-items: unsafe center; justify-content: unsafe center; width: 271px; height: 1px; padding-top: 823px; margin-left: 1215px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 0; text-align: center; color: #333333; "><div style="display: inline-block; font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; color: #333333; line-height: 1.2; pointer-events: all; white-space: normal; word-wrap: normal; "><div style=""><b style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><font style="color: rgb(255, 0, 255);">Besorgerprozess</font></b></div><div style=""><b style="background-color: transparent;"><div style="font-weight: 400;"><div style=""><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Eine Teilabgabe mit</span></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400;">Packungsanzahl: 0<b></b></div><div style="font-weight: 400;"><font color="#000000" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Typ: </font><span style="color: rgb(204, 102, 0); background-color: transparent;">First Fill - Part Fill </span><span style="color: rgb(204, 102, 0); background-color: transparent;"><font style="color: rgb(51, 0, 26);">ODER </font></span><span style="color: rgb(204, 102, 0); background-color: transparent;">Refill Fill - Part Fill </span><font style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="background-color: transparent;">ODER </span><font style="background-color: transparent;"> </font></font><span style="color: rgb(0, 153, 0); background-color: transparent;">Refill - Complete</span></div></b><b style="background-color: transparent;"><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400;"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));">Status: </span><b style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 255);">completed</b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400;"><b style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 255);"><div style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-weight: 400;"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">-&gt; dokumentiert eine Bestellung oder </span></div><div style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-weight: 400;"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Zubereitung von Arzneimitteln</span><span style="background-color: transparent;"></span></div><div style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-weight: 400;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">-&gt; möglich bei allen Arten von Teilabgaben</span></div></b></div></b></div></div></div></div></foreignObject><image x="1215" y="758.5" width="271" height="133" xlink:href="data:image/png;base64,"/></switch></g></g></g><g data-cell-id="4ui51u9nk6TVf3VnQzT0-131"><g transform="translate(0.5,0.5)"><path d="M 1088.68 1104.36 L 1187 1104.43 L 1187 220 L 777 220 L 777 431.13" fill="none" stroke="#000000" stroke-miterlimit="10" pointer-events="stroke" style="stroke: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));"/><path d="M 777 436.38 L 773.5 429.38 L 777 431.13 L 780.5 429.38 Z" fill="#000000" stroke="#000000" stroke-miterlimit="10" pointer-events="all" style="fill: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); stroke: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));"/></g></g><g data-cell-id="4ui51u9nk6TVf3VnQzT0-139"><g transform="translate(0.5,0.5)"><path d="M 777 537.5 L 777 610.13" fill="none" stroke="#000000" stroke-miterlimit="10" pointer-events="stroke" style="stroke: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));"/><path d="M 777 615.38 L 773.5 608.38 L 777 610.13 L 780.5 608.38 Z" fill="#000000" stroke="#000000" stroke-miterlimit="10" pointer-events="all" style="fill: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); stroke: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));"/></g><g data-cell-id="4ui51u9nk6TVf3VnQzT0-337"><g><g><switch><foreignObject style="overflow: visible; text-align: left;" pointer-events="none" width="100%" height="100%" requiredFeatures="http://www.w3.org/TR/SVG11/feature#Extensibility"><div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="display: flex; align-items: unsafe center; justify-content: unsafe center; width: 1px; height: 1p